# Umo Editor Fork — Project Context

This is a fork of [Umo Editor](https://github.com/umodoc/editor) — a WYSIWYG document editor built on Vue 3 + Tiptap 3, customized for 7eminar.

## Documentation

Project Wiki lives in `documentation/`. Read `documentation/index.md` first — it contains a map of all documentation files and guidance on which to read for your current task.

Key files:
- `documentation/architecture.md` — high-level architecture, tech stack, component tree, exposed API
- `documentation/extensions.md` — Tiptap extensions system + custom extensions
- `documentation/components.md` — Vue component structure (toolbar, menus, statusbar)
- `documentation/composables-and-state.md` — composables, state management, provide/inject
- `documentation/options-and-config.md` — configuration system, options schema
- `documentation/build-and-dev.md` — Vite build, auto-import, linting
- `documentation/localization.md` — i18n, locales, adding translations

Load documentation on-demand — only read files relevant to your current task.
